lead_paragraph: Max Verstappen will have an unhindered view of the first corner at the start of Sunday’s Belgian Formula One Grand Prix, but the Dutchman will have his sights set far beyond that after securing the maiden front-row start of his fledgling career.

headline.print_headline: Maiden Front Row Start Stokes Hopes of Verstappen Victory
